title: Plat III Support - LFT/Duo

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
Looking for a semi serious team looking to make Plat/Diamond+ in the preseason and next season. Have played in quite a few 5s teams, but only a few reached Plat. 
Also looking for a pretty chill Plat+ ADC main to duo with. Cheers.

replies.body: adc/jung main hit me up Delushunz
